00:39:31.290 --> 00:39:33.780
Here I'll a draw a tetrahedron
because that's simple.

00:39:33.780 --> 00:39:36.900
In this case, it's abstract,
so all of these edges

00:39:36.900 --> 00:39:37.670
are unit lengths.

00:39:37.670 --> 00:39:38.836
It's kind of like TreeMaker.

00:39:38.836 --> 00:39:40.510
You separately
